<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Worser" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Worser,</orth> == worse; 1) adj.: <bibl n="shak. luc 249" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 249</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 249" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 249</bibl> <bibl n="shak. luc 249" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 249</bibl> <bibl n="shak. son 144.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 144, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 3, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.208" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 208</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.36" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 3, 36</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.102" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 102</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.3.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 3, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 108</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.4.157" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 4, 157</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.222" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 222</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.7" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 7, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 1.2.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. I, 2, 64</bibl>.<lb />2) adv.: <cit><quote>how do you now, lieutenant? The w. that you give me the addition,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 1, 105</bibl></cit>. == less (cf. <emph>Worse</emph>): <cit><quote>the w. welcome,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 95</bibl></cit>. == more: <cit><quote>I cannot hate thee w. than I do,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 2.5.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 5, 90</bibl></cit>.
